{"tid":58293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"蒜頭愛好者入","createTime":"2016-12-28T16:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T13:17:48.000Z","uid":70317,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab303935164352e376680a06fb1cadf2ebbd793","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"我除咗就咁成舊生食，仲會浸豉油/甜醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成舊食嗰種感覺真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地鍾意點食？"},{"pid":"a6264f998b1c3bad73f075a101dfd619176b4e38","tid":58293,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒菜個種"},{"pid":"8c980658a60f9162dd2872b7609861eb5457b0f7","tid":58293,"uid":59731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"我中意生蒜，打邊爐整豉油會落勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔中意乾蒜，炒菜d蒜都唔錯"},{"pid":"b182b6fb2b579af442cf45503b92b9f63c50e8ba","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒菜個種</blockquote><br />\n其實我就點都鍾意食架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你入嚟理下我"},{"pid":"2facd4f57283a43e32b8d09cc0a2c399bb30dc03","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我中意生蒜，打邊爐整豉油會落勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔中意乾蒜，炒菜d蒜都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n乾嘅我都鍾意，但都係鍾意生嘅多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次同朋友出街食野想瘋狂食蒜嗰陣都會俾人制止，話我口會有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有摺喺屋企食"},{"pid":"3e9385477e77f3f083afb06d558e47ff49566106","tid":58293,"uid":46624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我中意生蒜，打邊爐整豉油會落勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔中意乾蒜，炒菜d蒜都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n乾嘅我都鍾意，但都係鍾意生嘅多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次同朋友出街食野想瘋狂食蒜嗰陣都會俾人制止，話我口會有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有摺喺屋企食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完啲胃氣又重<br />\n食親都比人屌"},{"pid":"2c0004ab949a937bfda9c95ca813c771be5d5038","tid":58293,"uid":8343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"好似話食蒜頭會殺菌<br />\n但食得多會好大體味 好臭<br />\n係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bff87b3405f1c8f4aa7b177922061366d6a89e","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我中意生蒜，打邊爐整豉油會落勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔中意乾蒜，炒菜d蒜都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n乾嘅我都鍾意，但都係鍾意生嘅多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次同朋友出街食野想瘋狂食蒜嗰陣都會俾人制止，話我口會有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有摺喺屋企食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完啲胃氣又重<br />\n食親都比人屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊匿喺屋企食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8707c6abd9e23268ba2801c286d8d1ca00a92299","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話食蒜頭會殺菌<br />\n但食得多會好大體味 好臭<br />\n係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知係咪真<br />\n暫時未有呢個情況發生喺我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd901b9a75df51247522ce1fabe415b37fb7a48","tid":58293,"uid":16882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"個口會好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632aec39bd2415f6d794d43d24a3b09ccfc39e4","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個口會好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我又鍾意食"},{"pid":"8e74d467d3ad227b86e10ca48558a2dbbdb9ec48","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個口會好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我又鍾意食</blockquote><br />\n如果喺街我會食完少講野，同埋係咁食薄荷糖<br />\n喺屋企冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3ae72037eb32cf1a55bd31260067de325d8637","tid":58293,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"炸蒜片當薯片食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f4ef35dc89886dc0342cece314a816192a8a41","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炸蒜片當薯片食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用匙羹嚟食"},{"pid":"6f06c8adbb004c496c1002c76d9b9db781c7de9b","tid":58293,"uid":62442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"勁中意<br />\n咩都撈蒜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b79bd63856bb678ef09049fe881eb50f5c4b9a","tid":58293,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"秋葉原有間叫秋葉原 有生蒜蓉比你任加<br />\n果次去食左人半樽 啖啖都充滿蒜蓉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor