-28T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個口會好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刷完牙個口都仲有陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用埋漱口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再唔得就刷多次</blockquote><br />\n朝早食完夜晚胃氣都仲有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1227e0ed36cb631692bfacafe3c7748adcea88ac","tid":58293,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個口會好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刷完牙個口都仲有陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用埋漱口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再唔得就刷多次</blockquote><br />\n朝早食完夜晚胃氣都仲有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好變態，幾鍾意浸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔影響到人我就唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前喺7仔見到有賣去除食完蒜之類嘅胃氣嘅綠色丸，我用唔着未買過，你地有冇試過？"}]}